Brilliance is fleeting. 13-Jun-21 06:32 PM
It's the kitchen for the buffet. Only accessible after you pass through the #buffet, this is a place where people seem to cook for the buffet. It's a rather large kitchen, similar to the ones you'd see with multiple cooks working together at a 5 star restaurant. Multiple industrial sinks are spread throughout the kitchen, as well as advanced ovens for the cooks to use. The equipment here is top notch, rivalled by nothing else. More or less any type of equipment is here, save for a few obscure ones. It seems you'll be able to make anything that you want. An island is in the center for the cooks to pass dishes around and set up for the buffet. Some carts with trays are near the back corner as well for waiters to push out and restock the main buffet. On top of that, there's the huge freezer. It's more like a closet, with the room's temperature set way down in order to hold all types of meats and fruits. More or less any type of raw ingredient you could wish for is here, all for you all to use. (edited)
